    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of a variety of synthetic resins, produced by the esterification of a polybasic acid with a polyhydric alcohol. Often used for coatings, finishes, adhesives, and molding compounds.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
